I'm already on the Marketplace page (the URL is '/admin/marketplace/index/'), which means I've already reached the goal of navigating to the Marketplace to find partners and extensions. I can see information about Platinum Partners, featured partners like Yotpo, Akeneo PIM, Vertex, and dotmailer, as well as links to visit Magento Marketplaces. Since I've already accomplished the goal of navigating to the Marketplace, I should inform the user.
